# READEME

Files: 
- aust-tiplabels: a file with nice tip labels for the austronesian phylogeny
- figure-1a: kinship terminology figure
- figure-1a-square: kinship terminology figure alternative
- figure-2.svg: phylogenies and transition graph svg 
- g15693.png: png of figure 2
- figure-helper: helper functions for making figures
- hypothesis table: csv file for table S2
- map: script for a making a map graphic
- mirrored-coevolution-plots: plots of each co-evolutionary hypothesis on mirrored phylogenies
- phylogeny.R: code to create mirrored phylogenies
- table-1: csv and code to make table 1 in the text
- terminology-map: global map of societies coloured by terminology type
- transition network: code to make the transition graph
- transition-network3.svg: svg for transition network
- uto-tiplabels: nice tiplabes for uto aztecan